  summaries:
    lowAffinitySummary: Neo left still wound tight, frustration simmering beneath
      the surface. Your drink didn't reach him tonight. The Tower card flickers dimly
      - chaos unresolved, transformation delayed.
    mediumAffinitySummary: Neo seemed lighter when he left, even if just a little.
      Your drink helped take the edge off. The Tower card glows softly - the first
      crack in the walls he's built around himself.
    highAffinitySummary: Neo lingered a moment before leaving, something close to
      peace in his eyes. You offered exactly what he needed. The Tower card burns
      bright - you're helping him find solid ground in the rubble.
